  "detailed_description": "<h1>Buzz</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/663090/extras/cb2cb60d3a16ef0d4c1bf81b50a6360c.avif?t=1754028867\" width=614 height=736 /></span><br><strong>Character Encyclopedia now available on our Official Website!</strong><br>Come take a look to know more about your favorite characters!</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Characteristics</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> More than 200 game characters<br></li><li> Active automatic hunting mode for gameplay support<br></li><li> Control up to 3 characters simultaneously<br></li><li> More than 300 extensive areas to explore<br></li><li> Up to more than 3,000 different quests<br></li><li> Over 3,000 types of weapons, armor and costumes<br></li><li> More than 190 different missions, with over 7,000 types of regular monsters and over 100 types of raid monsters<br></li><li> Real-time faction wars with Clique Battles, Colony Wars and other PvP and RvR contents<br></li><li> Elegant, medieval Europe-inspired graphics<br></li><li> More than 200 alluring background tracks</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Characteristics</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> More than 200 game characters<br></li><li> Active automatic hunting mode for gameplay support<br></li><li> Control up to 3 characters simultaneously<br></li><li> More than 300 extensive areas to explore<br></li><li> Up to more than 3,000 different quests<br></li><li> Over 3,000 types of weapons, armor and costumes<br></li><li> More than 190 different missions, with over 7,000 types of regular monsters and over 100 types of raid monsters<br></li><li> Real-time faction wars with Clique Battles, Colony Wars and other PvP and RvR contents<br></li><li> Elegant, medieval Europe-inspired graphics<br></li><li> More than 200 alluring background tracks</li></ul>",
